# SCIMServer code ownership.
#
# Each line is a path pattern followed by one or more GitHub usernames or team
# names. The LAST matching pattern wins. GitHub auto-requests review from the
# owners on every PR that touches a matching path. Combined with branch
# protection on master, ownership becomes a soft enforcement of the standing
# rule: every change goes through a designated reviewer.
#
# Closes OPS-4 (DELIVERY_PLAN.md Week 1 Day 5).
#
# When adding a contributor, add them as a NEW owner alongside @pranems on the
# specific paths they own; do not silently replace.

# Default owner for everything in the repo (catches new top-level files).
*                                @pranems

# Production code
/api/                            @pranems

# Web client
/web/                            @pranems

# Infrastructure (Bicep, deploy scripts, container manifests)
/infra/                          @pranems
/scripts/                        @pranems
/Dockerfile                      @pranems
/Dockerfile.optimized            @pranems
/Dockerfile.ultra                @pranems
/docker-compose.yml              @pranems
/docker-compose.debug.yml        @pranems

# CI / governance / GitHub config
/.github/                        @pranems

# Living documentation
/docs/                           @pranems
/Session_starter.md              @pranems
/CHANGELOG.md                    @pranems
/README.md                       @pranems
/DEPLOYMENT.md                   @pranems
/admin.md                        @pranems
